oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Lt. Col. J.Y. Kinsall with unidentified U.S. Air Force soldiers and Japanese men
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of Lt. Col. J.Y. Kinsall with two unidentified men in United States Air Force uniforms and 10 Japanese men, taken near Tokyo, Japan. The men are posing for a group photograph and Kinsall is pictured in the first row, in the middle with two men on both his left and right side. Each of the Japanese males signed their names on the photograph.
